hopobject.name: Logg-Dogg
hopobject.http_browser: Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 8.0; Windows NT 6.0; Trident/4.0; GTB6; SLCC1; .NET CLR 2.0.50727; Media Center PC 5.0; MDDC; .NET CLR 3.5.30729; .NET CLR 3.0.30729)
hopobject.body: Logg-Dogg will be an independent data logging system with ecu interface targeted toward the weekend warrior drag racer. The system will take advantage of some pre-existing vehicle sensors while additional sensors will be installed into the vehicle. Logg-Dogg will also utilize GPS technology to allow drivers to estimate quarter/eighth mile track times. An Arduino will be the interface board for a/d sensors and miscellaneous i/o interfaces.
hopobject.shortdesc: Data logger for automotive racing applications.
